These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, camping, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, sports, musical
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, roller, car, helicopter
1. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the helicopter is between the person watching musical movies and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing      | baking | magic-tricks | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | fantasy  | mystery   | musical    |
| Transport     | taxi     | car    | helicopter    | roller      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, card-games, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, indonesian, italian, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, ship
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the italian##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the indonesian##1
7. the nigerian is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
8. the egyptian is between the indonesian and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | card-games   | gardening | filmmaking  |
| Nationality   | italian     | nigerian | egyptian  | indonesian |
| Transport     | ship        | roller  | quad-bike    | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, apricot, artichoke, cabbage
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, mexican, brazilian, indonesian
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bike, car, taxi
1. the indonesian is between the person eating cherry and the person eating cabbage##2
2. the mexican is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the boat is the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
6. the brazilian is between the person eating apricot and the japanese##2
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | cherry | apricot   | cabbage     | artichoke     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | indonesian | brazilian   | japanese  |
| Transport     | taxi      | bike | car | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, musical, western, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, indie, classical, dubstep
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball, ice-hockey, parkour
1. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
2. the person watching musical movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
5. the fan of dubstep is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person watching western movies is the fan of country##1
7. the fan of classical is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | family   | western     | musical |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | dubstep      | country        | indie     |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | volleyball | parkour | baseball   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, polish, italian, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, tennis, water-polo, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, trike, subway
1. the thai is the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the italian is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bike is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
7. the polish is on the far right##1
8. the italian is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
9. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | french   | thai   | italian | polish |
| Sport         | tennis      | parkour | soccer      | water-polo |
| Transport     | skateboard | bike        | subway       | trike  |

