.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, orange, nectarine, eggplant
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, traveling, card-games
4 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, goat, mouse
1. the person eating orange is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the owner of the horse is the person eating orange##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating orange##1
7. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | nectarine   | eggplant      | orange       | artichoke |
| Hobby   | dancing | card-games | traveling     | singing |
| Pet     | mouse     | lizard  | horse | goat |

