.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, coffee, cola
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie, animation, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit, fish, cat
1. the owner of the fish is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching fantasy movies and the owner of the mouse##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
5. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking juice##1
8. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee   | cola          | mirinda | juice        |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | zombie | fantasy   | thriller     |
| Pet           | mouse | rabbit         | cat         | fish |

