.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, woodworking, video-games, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, freelancer, doctor, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, reggae, dubstep, salsa
1. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
2. the doctor is the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the project-manager is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the fan of reggae is between the entrepreneur and the person who's hobby is camping##2
6. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the doctor##3
7. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is video-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | camping      | video-games       | fishing    |
| Job           | freelancer  | doctor  | project-manager | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | dubstep | reggae         | jazz    |

