.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, almond-milk, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, mechanic, police-officer, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tea-polo, snowboarding, tennis, lacrosse
1. the journalist is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the journalist##3
3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the journalist##3
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the journalist##1
7. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the mechanic is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the chef is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | sprite         | 7up  | almond-milk     | tea         |
| Job        | chef | mechanic | journalist | police-officer         |
| Sport      | snowboarding         | tennis  | tea-polo   | lacrosse |

