.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, trance, classical, jazz
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, polish, spanish
4 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, snake, rabbit
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 2. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 4. the polish is between the fan of trance and the fan of folk##2
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
 6. the owner of the rabbit is the fan of classical##1
 7. the spanish is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 9. the brazilian is between the fan of jazz and the fan of classical##2
10. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | classical    | trance | jazz    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish | brazilian  | spanish |
| Pet           | snake   | rabbit    | turtle        | fish   |

