.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, sprite, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, engineer, coach, mechanic
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, german, australian, french
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
2. the engineer is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the french is on the left or right of the coach##3
4. the engineer is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the lawyer##1
6. the french is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the german is on the left of the engineer##1
8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the german##3
9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | cola                | water  | lemonade | sprite   |
| Job           | mechanic | engineer | lawyer   | coach |
| Nationality   | german         | brazilian     | french     | australian |

