.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, pineapple, kiwi, garlic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, family, documentary, horror
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, rock, funk, reggae
1. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the fan of pop is between the person watching horror movies and the fan of reggae##2
6. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | kiwi    | pineapple  | garlic  | grapes |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | family | disaster | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | pop     | reggae    | rock |

