.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, mirinda, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, french, american
4 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, chinchilla, lizard
1. the owner of the frog is between the person drinking mirinda and the dutch##2
2. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
3. the french is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the egyptian##1
5. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
7. the dutch is on the left or right of the american##3
8. the french is the person drinking cola##1
9. the american is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola | mirinda      | 7up  | iced-tea    |
| Nationality   | french   | egyptian | american | dutch |
| Pet           | lizard      | chinchilla       | frog   | ferret      |

