.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, traveling, baking, card-games
There are 4 different nationalities: german, colombian, russian, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, cricket, biathlon
1. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's sport is basketball##2
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the french is between the person who's sport is basketball and the german##2
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | singing    | baking | traveling  | card-games  |
| Nationality   | russian | colombian       | french | german |
| Sport         | cricket   | basketball      | biathlon | rowing       |

