4. the person drinking fanta is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking lemonade##1

