.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, sprite, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, ice-hockey, cycling, biathlon
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, trike, tram
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person driving the bus and the person who's sport is cycling##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | sprite    | lemonade     | 7up    | coffee        |
| Sport       | cycling   | sailing | ice-hockey | biathlon |
| Transport   | tram | trike      | bus    | helicopter   |

