3. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3
5. the argentine is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the person eating artichoke is in an odd position##4
7. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating kiwi is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
