.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, banana, peach, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, gardening, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, turtle, rabbit
1. the person eating pineapple is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
4. the person eating peach is on the far left##1
5. the person eating banana is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
8. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | peach    | banana    | pineapple  | strawberry |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku | chess | gardening      |
| Pet     | fish   | ferret        | rabbit   | turtle       |

 